/PSL_clip {clip /PSL_nclip PSL_nclip 1 add def} def
/PSL_eoclip {eoclip /PSL_nclip PSL_nclip 1 add def} def
/PSL_cliprestore {cliprestore /PSL_nclip PSL_nclip 1 sub def} def
